text: Great work at the training camp, Mamimi.

Thanks for managing to work hard all the way through,
somehow or another.

Were you perhaps expecting me to give up
halfway through, Producer?

...Well it's not like I had ruled
out that possibility though...

But in the end,
you perservered all the way through.

── Didn't you end up coming to like this location afterall,
Mamimi?

Well, I did get to sleep more than usual,
and it ended up feeling better than I expected I guess.

Fufuu,
Maybe I should just start living here.

R-Really...?
I wouldn't stop you though...

...Of course, if you decided to live out here
it would be quite the ordeal to bring you to jobs...
...Well, you don't need to think that seriously about it or anything.
